<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 space-y-8">
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">PEG（市盈增长比）知识库</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">PEG 用“增长”来修正 PE：同样的 PE，对应更快的增长通常意味着估值压力更小。PEG 的关键在于增长口径是否真实、可持续。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm">
            <a href="/kb" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">知识库</a>
            <span class="text-gray-300 mx-2">/</span>
            <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">股票列表</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">1. PEG 是什么？</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>PEG（Price/Earnings to Growth）常见写法：PEG = PE / 增长率。</p>
            <p>直观理解：市场给了你一个 PE，同时你还要问一句“这个盈利能以多快速度增长”。增长越快，PEG 越低。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">常见口径</div>
            <div>PE：通常用 PE(TTM)。</div>
            <div>增长率：常用净利润同比（YoY）、扣非净利润同比、或未来 3-5 年盈利复合增速（预测）。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">2. PEG 适合看什么？不适合看什么？</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-green-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-1">更适合</div>
                <div>成长逻辑清晰、盈利扩张可持续的行业（例如软件/服务、品牌消费、部分制造龙头）。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">不太适合</div>
                <div>强周期、利润大起大落或一次性收益占比高的公司：同比会“忽高忽低”，PEG 容易失真。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">3. 常见坑</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">同比为负 / 接近 0</div>
                <div>增长为负时，PEG 失去“用增长修正估值”的意义；增长接近 0 时，PEG 会被放大，容易产生误判。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">基数效应</div>
                <div>上年利润很低导致今年同比暴增，PEG 可能极低，但不代表长期成长性真的那么强。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">一次性因素</div>
                <div>资产处置、补贴、投资收益等会让净利同比短期扭曲，建议优先看扣非口径或结合现金流。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-100 rounded-lg p-4 text-yellow-900/90 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <div class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-1">高 PE + 高增长</div>
                <div>即使 PEG 看起来“合理”，高 PE 仍意味着预期很满，估值容错率较低，需要更多确定性。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4. 本系统里的 PEG 计算口径</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-2 text-sm">
            <div>PEG = PE(TTM) / 净利同比(%)。</div>
            <div>净利同比优先使用扣非净利同比（若有），否则使用净利润同比。</div>
            <div>当净利同比 ≤ 0 或 PE ≤ 0 时，PEG 不显示（用 PEG 等级标记“负增长/不可用”）。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">5. PEG 等级（PEG Level）</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">1 极低估成长</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(PEG &lt; 0.5)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">2 优质成长</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(0.5 - 1)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">3 合理</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(1 - 1.5)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">4 偏贵</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(&gt; 1.5)</span></div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-3 md:col-span-2"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">5 负增长</span> <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(净利同比 &lt; 0)</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">使用建议</div>
            <div>PEG Level 适合快速分组筛选；真正决策仍建议结合商业模式、毛利/费用结构、现金流、ROE 与负债水平一起判断。</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
        <div>提示：以上内容仅用于解释指标与方法论，不构成任何投资建议。市场有风险，决策需自担。</div>
    </section>
</div>
